Package payroll_processing_system.application

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Company
    Company class is a container class that is designed to hold Employee objects and any subclasses of Employee.
    Date
    Date class provides the structure for the Date object, which contains a year, month and day.
    Employee
    Employee class represents an abstract data type Employee, which models any employee in a real life situation.
    Fulltime
    Fulltime Class is a child class of Employee, and represents a Full-time employee with additional instance variable Salary.
    IoFields
    IoFields class contains String messages that are used to display info about user commands that are handled by the PayrollProcessing class
    Main
    Main class extends javafx application class and connects the model, view and controller
    Management
    Management class is a child class of Fulltime and represents a Management Employee with additional instance variables roleName, roleCode, and additionalComp.
    Parttime
    Parttime is a child class of Employee, and represents a Part-time employee with additional instance variables hourlyRate, overtimeRate, and hours
    Profile
    Defines the profile of an employee with a name, department, and dateHired.
